Revision history for Plack-Middleware-NeverExpire

1.006 Sat 10 Jan 2015
	- No functional changes
	- No longer contains INSTALL file with install-as-root instructions

1.005 Sun 04 Jan 2015
	- Be strict about no imports.

1.004 Sun 03 Feb 2013
	- Add `public` to the Cache-Control header so non-expiry is ensured even over SSL.

1.003 Tue 01 Mar 2011
	- Declare dependecy on Plack 0.9942. No functional changes.

1.002 Fri 18 Feb 2011
	- Switched to using `response_cb`.

1.001 Thu 17 Feb 2011
	- Declared depenencies. No functional changes.

1.0 Thu 17 Feb 2011
	- Initial release.
